":0,"content":"假设我要买一箱乒乓球，有一个供应商提供了 10 箱给我挑，并且告诉我：\r\n\r\n这 10 箱是同一批生产的，每箱 100 个，次品率 30%。\r\n\r\n装箱工人无法分辨次品，也就是说装箱是随机的，装完后工人从每箱随机取了 3 个在外面供挑选，其他 97 个封在箱子里不能打开挑选。\r\n\r\n现在的问题是：\r\n\r\n通过挑选每箱的三个样品，对最终购买结果会有影响么？","content_rendered":"<p>假设我要买一箱乒乓球，有一个供应商提供了 10 箱给我挑，并且告诉我：</p>\n<p>这 10 箱是同一批生产的，每箱 100 个，次品率 30%。</p>\n<p>装箱工人无法分辨次品，也就是说装箱是随机的，装完后工人从每箱随机取了 3 个在外面供挑选，其他 97 个封在箱子里不能打开挑选。</p>\n<p>现在的问题是：</p>\n<p>通过挑选每箱的三个样品，对最终购买结果会有影响么？</p>\n","last_modified":1673841026,"replies":11,"id":909230},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1673261684","name":"programmer","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1673261684","title":"程序员","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","topics":52951,"footer":"","header":"While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.","title_alternative":"Programmer","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1673261684","stars":8159,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":300,"parent_node_name":"computer"},"member":{"id":587457,"username":"subframe75361","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/subframe75361","website":"","twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":"","tagline":"","bio":"","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b115/3d02/587457_mini.png?m=1673837359","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b115/3d02/587457_normal.png?m=1673837359","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b115/3d02/587457_large.png?m=1673837359","avatar_xlarge":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b115/3d02/587457_xlarge.png?m=1673837359","avatar_xxlarge":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b115/3d02/587457_xlarge.png?m=1673837359","avatar_xxxlarge":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b115/3d02/587457_xlarge.png?m=1673837359","created":1657357117,"last_modified":1673837359},"last_reply_by":"lysS","last_touched":1673841081,"title":"请教一下， clash for windows 如何做到后台内存占用比较低的","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/909205","created":1673837585,"deleted":0,"content":"![]( https://i.328888